  <li><strong>Sketch</strong> — the built-in text tool includes a "Populate with Lorem Ipsum" option in the context menu.</li>
  <li><strong>Adobe XD</strong> — right-click a text element and choose "Replace with Lorem Ipsum".</li>
  <li><strong>VS Code</strong> — the Emmet abbreviation <code>lorem</code> expands to a lorem ipsum paragraph. <code>lorem5</code> gives you 5 words, <code>lorem100</code> gives 100 words.</li>
</ul>

